      • setProjectFields

        public void setProjectFields(java.util.List<com.behance.sdk.dto.BehanceSDKCreativeFieldDTO> projectFields)
        Sets the creative fields of the project being published. To use this API : Get the list (creativeFieldList) from AdobeUXBehanceWorkflow::getCreativeFields() and use that to create the required list of creative-fields Note : Don't set this field directly using creativeFieldsList.subList(x,y).The sublist() method returns a List, which is not necessarily an ArrayList (It can be actually a RandomAccessSublist, because of which the API could crash).
        Parameters:
        projectFields - the fields for the project.
